info.description:
JSYNC - Full Data Serialization in JSON
---------------------------------------

Installation
------------

Use::

    > sudo pip install jsync

or::

    > sudo easy install jsync

or::

    > git clone git://github.com/you/jsync-py.git
    > cd reparse-py
    > sudo make install

Usage
-----

Python code::

    import jsync

    string = jsync.dump(object)
    object = jsync.load(string)

Development Status
------------------

ALPHA
